billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO CULTURAL AFFAIRS, TOURISM, PARKS AND RECREATION

title: Requires tourism promotion agencies seeking matching economic development funds to have a program to encourage visitation of state parks and historic sites
summary: Requires tourism promotion agencies seeking matching economic development funds to have a program to encourage visitation of state parks and historic sites.
currentCommittee: CULTURAL AFFAIRS, TOURISM, PARKS AND RECREATION
actClause: AN ACT to amend the economic development law, in relation to the provision of matching funds to tourist promotion agencies for encouraging visitation to state parks and historic sites
